Presentations 4-5 Mar 2008
--------------------------
Bluetongue in Spain

As mentioned in our recent posting 20080522.1693, another emerging
orbivirus disease, namely Epizootic Hemorrhagic Disease (EHD), which
has the potential to affect cattle seriously, is suspected to have
advanced during 2007 in eastern Mediterranean territories which are
closer to south-eastern Europe. A request for information is pending. - Mod.AS]
